General.Name: Mangold Fondkommission AB
General.Description: Mangold Fondkommission AB provides financial services to companies, institutions, and private individuals in Sweden. It operates in two segments, Investment Banking and Private Banking. The company offers investment banking services, such as corporate finance, merger and acquisition, issuing, research, certified adviser, Nordic Growth Market mentoring, liquidity, and qualified advisor services. It also private banking services, such as wealth advisory; securities trading; and portfolio management services. The company was incorporated in 2000 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden. Mangold Fondkommission AB is a subsidiary of Mangold AB.
